PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1985-1/1621 which will permit the Minister to enter into Agreements with Indian Bands for the repayment of housing loans guaranteed by the Minister under the INDIAN ON-RESERVE LOAN GUARANTEE PROGRAM and to adjust the original interest rates.
